README for xfce4-appfinder
==============================================

WHAT IS IT?
-----------
Xfce4 Appfinder is an useful software that permits you to find every
application in the system supporting Desktop entry format.

WHAT CAN I DO WITH IT?
----------------------
Search for "lost" software, add entries to xfdesktop menu,
add launchers to the panel (not yet :-) and obviously run the selected
software from it.

SOMETHING MORE?
---------------
Please check TODO file ;-)

